01:37:16,039 --> 01:37:18,039
Yeah, totally.

2352
01:37:18,039 --> 01:37:23,039
Makoth, I will return to learn more

2353
01:37:23,039 --> 01:37:27,039
when we have defeated the Cult of the Dragon.

2354
01:37:27,039 --> 01:37:29,039
I guess that's when I'll return.

2355
01:37:29,039 --> 01:37:33,039
I feel you will find more of your abilities along your journey,

2356
01:37:33,039 --> 01:37:38,039
but we would be grateful to help you in discovering those.

2357
01:37:38,039 --> 01:37:41,039
Thank you for your help.

2358
01:37:43,039 --> 01:37:44,039
To the airship.

2359
01:37:44,039 --> 01:37:46,039
To the airship.

2360
01:37:46,039 --> 01:37:50,039
To everyone's favorite, Grancis.

2361
01:37:50,039 --> 01:37:53,039
To the man everyone hates for some reason.

2362
01:37:53,039 --> 01:37:54,039
For some reason.

2363
01:37:54,039 --> 01:37:55,039
Krystrel Zoid's very lovable.

2364
01:37:55,039 --> 01:37:57,039
I don't know why everyone just loves him.

2365
01:37:57,039 --> 01:37:59,039
He could just be an intense personality.

2366
01:37:59,039 --> 01:38:04,039
You make your way back out and you meet the same dwarf at the gate.

2367
01:38:04,039 --> 01:38:05,039
Knock, knock.

2368
01:38:05,039 --> 01:38:07,039
Is he leaving this time?

2369
01:38:07,039 --> 01:38:08,039
Yes.

2370
01:38:08,039 --> 01:38:09,039
Good.

2371
01:38:09,039 --> 01:38:10,039
We're going to go.

2372
01:38:10,039 --> 01:38:11,039
We're going to take Grancis with us.

2373
01:38:11,039 --> 01:38:12,039
Alright.

2374
01:38:12,039 --> 01:38:13,039
Alright.

2375
01:38:13,039 --> 01:38:14,039
He lets you in.

2376
01:38:14,039 --> 01:38:17,039
He gives us whatever we want from the dwarf's trouble.

2377
01:38:17,039 --> 01:38:19,039
Anything you guys need?

2378
01:38:19,039 --> 01:38:22,039
You need some weapons, some armor, some something?

2379
01:38:22,039 --> 01:38:24,039
You got anything cool?

2380
01:38:24,039 --> 01:38:28,039
I mean, it's all like ore and stuff, but I don't know.

2381
01:38:28,039 --> 01:38:29,039
You're fine.

2382
01:38:29,039 --> 01:38:30,039
Just get out of here.

2383
01:38:30,039 --> 01:38:31,039
That's all I'm saying.

2384
01:38:31,039 --> 01:38:33,039
So yeah, he just lets you through

2385
01:38:33,039 --> 01:38:35,039
and sees you climb aboard the airship.

2386
01:38:35,039 --> 01:38:36,039
And Grancis says,

2387
01:38:36,039 --> 01:38:38,039
Alright, so we can...

2388
01:38:38,039 --> 01:38:42,039
She's already gone, but can we get out of here now?

2389
01:38:42,039 --> 01:38:44,039
Yeah, I don't see why not.

2390
01:38:44,039 --> 01:38:45,039
Let's go.

2391
01:38:45,039 --> 01:38:46,039
Alright, so he...

2392
01:38:46,039 --> 01:38:47,039
Let's go find a dragon mask.

2393
01:38:47,039 --> 01:38:50,039
He starts pulling knobs and levers.

2394
01:38:50,039 --> 01:38:53,039
He's like, are we going to go see your horses or what?

2395
01:38:53,039 --> 01:38:54,039
Yeah, the horses.

2396
01:38:54,039 --> 01:38:57,039
Quick stop by the horses?

2397
01:38:57,039 --> 01:38:59,039
I have no idea of the geography of this place.

2398
01:38:59,039 --> 01:39:00,039
I only have a map of the city.

2399
01:39:00,039 --> 01:39:03,039
We left them in a forest

2400
01:39:03,039 --> 01:39:07,039
before we found the Oni, the kid that was the Oni,

2401
01:39:07,039 --> 01:39:08,039
if I remember correctly.

2402
01:39:08,039 --> 01:39:09,039
Oh, so that wasn't that far.

2403
01:39:09,039 --> 01:39:11,039
That was like less than a day's walk.

2404
01:39:11,039 --> 01:39:13,039
How fast does this airship go?

2405
01:39:13,039 --> 01:39:14,039
Quick, perfect.

2406
01:39:14,039 --> 01:39:15,039
We're there.

2407
01:39:15,039 --> 01:39:17,039
Grancis turns all the knobs and everything

2408
01:39:17,039 --> 01:39:19,039
and sets off towards Little Rock.

2409
01:39:19,039 --> 01:39:23,039
You see, along your way,

2410
01:39:23,039 --> 01:39:27,039
three recognizable horses riding in the field.

2411
01:39:27,039 --> 01:39:28,039
I scream out the ship,

2412
01:39:28,039 --> 01:39:29,039
Tiny!

2413
01:39:29,039 --> 01:39:31,039
He says, are we picking up these horses or what?

2414
01:39:31,039 --> 01:39:32,039
Fuck yeah.

2415
01:39:32,039 --> 01:39:35,039
So he drops the airship down and lowers a ramp.

2416
01:39:35,039 --> 01:39:39,039
And you guys lead the horses back onto the ship.

2417
01:39:39,039 --> 01:39:42,039
And he says, if they shit, I'm not cleaning it up.

2418
01:39:42,039 --> 01:39:44,039
Well, the horses, they're definitely going to shit.

2419
01:39:44,039 --> 01:39:46,039
Yeah, but I'm not cleaning it up is all I'm saying.

2420
01:39:46,039 --> 01:39:47,039
Fair.

2421
01:39:47,039 --> 01:39:48,039
But there's not really an if.

2422
01:39:48,039 --> 01:39:49,039
That's all we're saying.

2423
01:39:49,039 --> 01:39:50,039
When they shit, I'm not cleaning it up.

2424
01:39:50,039 --> 01:39:52,039
So just figure it out.

2425
01:39:52,039 --> 01:39:55,039
Also, I'm not bringing these guys back to that jackass guy.

2426
01:39:55,039 --> 01:39:57,039
And then he takes back off

2427
01:39:57,039 --> 01:40:02,039
and starts setting south towards these serpent hills.

2428
01:40:02,039 --> 01:40:04,039
Guys, we played D&D together.

2429
